column2: "/ci2 3 Ah, excellent. You, look after the tuna girl. I'll handle the fighting."
"/ci4 3 I'd rather be on my own. Tch... You're driving me insane."
"There's no helping it. Why don't we have something to eat before we go? Hey tuna girl, you've got some tuna there, right? Let's serve that as an appetizer."
"I'm just not used to fighting with allies..."
"Tch... You even drive me insane when you're quiet."
